casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jose W. VEGA.
No. D-2968.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 17, 2017.
Jose W. Vega, of Houston, Texas, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
